262
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:18,840
Miss!

263
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,440
Miss!

264
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:29,030
Miss!

265
00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:32,230
Miss!

266
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:41,560
